rows.label: tlk45420151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Alba Margen is pretty prosperous
right now, you know?

rows.label: tlk45420151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Anything you need, chances are
good you can buy it right here
in Ayvill Shopping District.

rows.label: tlk45420151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But cross Midorl Bridge and head out of
the capital, and it's a different story.
It's a barren wasteland out there.

rows.label: tlk45420151_01_msg0004
rows.name:
You'll want to be careful if you're
venturing out of the city. The
area isn't exactly hospitable.

rows.label: tlk45420151_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Also, I'd recommend you don't head
right after crossing the bridge. You
might run into a dangerous lot.
